text:
They reportedly ended their two-year romance in December - but Ellie Goulding and Dougie Poynter appear to be back on track.
The two musicians, both aged 28, were pictured picking up a late night spot of shopping from their local Waitrose on Thursday.
While they could just be friends, Dougie appeared keen to keep a low profile for the outing, wrapping his camouflage coat around his face as he made his way out into the street.
